<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>로그인 / 회원가입 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #111111;
      --text: #1f1f1f;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      --kakao: #FEE500;
      --naver: #03C75A;
      --max: 1280px;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--black);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }

    header {
      background: rgba(245, 243, 239, 0.88);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .header-inner {
      min-height: 82px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 82px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 0 70px;
    }

    .auth-layout {
      width: 100%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 26px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .visual-card,
    .auth-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .visual-card {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 680px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.48), rgba(0,0,0,0.10)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496747611176-843222e1e57c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
    }

    .visual-content {
      position: absolute;
      left: 42px;
      right: 42px;
      bottom: 42px;
      color: white;
    }

    .visual-content small {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .visual-content h1 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 64px);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .visual-content p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 430px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.84);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .auth-card {
      padding: 38px 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .auth-eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .auth-title {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 38px;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .auth-desc {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .benefit-box {
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .benefit-box strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .benefit-box span {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .button-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .social-btn,
    .line-btn {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 58px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .social-btn.kakao {
      background: var(--kakao);
      color: #191919;
    }

    .social-btn.naver {
      background: var(--naver);
      color: white;
    }

    .line-sep {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: #9a9389;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .line-sep::before,
    .line-sep::after {
      content: "";
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--line);
    }

    .line-btn.dark {
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
    }

    .line-btn.light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .auth-help {
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .auth-help strong {
      color: var(--black);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .auth-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .visual-card {
        min-height: 420px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .header-actions {
        display: none;
      }

      .visual-card,
      .auth-card {
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .visual-content {
        left: 24px;
        right: 24px;
        bottom: 24px;
      }

      .auth-card {
        padding: 26px 20px;
      }

      .auth-title {
        font-size: 30px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">DAMORE OFFICIAL ONLINE STORE</div>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <span class="brand-logo">DAMORE</span>
          <span class="brand-sub">the more, the mood</span>
        </a>

        <div class="header-actions">
          <a href="/order/lookup">주문조회</a>
          <a href="/login">로그인</a>
          <a href="/register">회원가입</a>
          <a href="/cart">장바구니 <%= typeof cartCount !== 'undefined' ? cartCount : 0 %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="auth-layout">
        <section class="visual-card">
          <div class="visual-content">
            <small>Damore Membership</small>
            <h1>더 편한 쇼핑, 더 빠른 주문</h1>
            <p>
              회원은 내 주문내역을 더 쉽게 확인할 수 있고,
              비회원도 주문은 가능하지만 로그인하면 더 자연스럽고 편하게 쇼핑할 수 있습니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="auth-card">
          <div class="auth-eyebrow">Start with DAMORE</div>
          <h2 class="auth-title">로그인 / 회원가입</h2>
          <p class="auth-desc">
            원하는 방식으로 시작하세요. 소셜로그인은 나중에 실제 연동만 붙이면 바로 확장할 수 있는 구조입니다.
          </p>

          <div class="benefit-box">
            <strong>회원 혜택</strong>
            <span>
              내 주문내역 확인, 더 빠른 재주문, 기본 정보 자동 입력 등
              쇼핑 흐름을 더 자연스럽게 사용할 수 있습니다.
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="button-stack">
            <a href="/auth/kakao" class="social-btn kakao">카카오로 계속하기</a>
            <a href="/auth/naver" class="social-btn naver">네이버로 계속하기</a>
          </div>

          <div class="line-sep">또는</div>

          <div class="button-stack">
            <a href="/login" class="line-btn dark">이메일로 로그인</a>
            <a href="/register" class="line-btn light">이메일로 회원가입</a>
          </div>

          <div class="auth-help">
            <strong>안내</strong><br />
            현재 카카오 / 네이버 버튼은 UI용 진입 버튼으로 먼저 만들어둔 상태다.<br />
            실제 연동 시 `/auth/kakao`, `/auth/naver` 라우트만 연결하면 된다.
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>